text: Jean-Paul Vergne (born 13 March 1970) is a French rower. He competed in the men's coxed four event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:French male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of France Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Lot-et-Garonne
